&lt;h1 id="having-kids"&gt;Having Kids&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;December 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before I had kids, I was afraid of having kids. Up to that point I felt about kids the way the young Augustine felt about living virtuously. I&amp;rsquo;d have been sad to think I&amp;rsquo;d never have children. But did I want them now? No.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Do What You Love</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/love/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/love/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/love/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
